dct_description_sm: Relief shown by form lines and spot heights. Some sheets show hachures. Principal meridian is Athens. Bookseller's label pasted on verso: K. Grēgouras & Sie., Athens. Κ. Γρεγουρας & Σια., Αθήναι. Maps were trimmed on sides, top and bottom. Map title, scale, and legend label are pasted on verso. Pasted on verso: "Topographikoi chartai tēs Hellados & Valkaniōn". Τοπογραφικοί χάρται της Ελλάδος & Βαλκανίων Title devised by cataloger.
